Wordpress Child Theme Code for 
Shelton Research Group
This repository follows the normal Wordpress directory structure:
Wordpress
   wp-content
      Themes
         ThemeNames, etc. 


Parent Theme              Changes
  - Magazine Basic
                          Allow for a header background image
                          Allow Taller header / logo
                          Allow for optional page-by-page or post-by-post comments
                          If comments are not allowed, just be quiet, dont say "Comments are not allowed"
                          Allow pages that contain posts of certain categories

